Package static_comp

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • static_comp.Edge

  • public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    Edge is a class used to represent a connection between two points, where it has a cost that is 1 by default. This class is used, for instance, to represent every connection in the grid and every move made by an individual (path) It is also used to represent a special zone once it was the needed fields.
